      • findContact

        ABContact findContact(String queryID)
        Returns the ABContact with the given ID/public ID. If the query string is an integer, then the method assumes it is an ID. Otherwise, the method assumes it is a public ID. If an ABContact with that ID or public ID cannot be found, it returns null. This method is used primarily in examples where a given contact is needed and the code that retrieves it ne ds to be as short as possible.
